    "from mlflow import MlflowClient\n",
    "\n",
    "client = MlflowClient(registry_uri=\"databricks-uc\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Find the version we just registered\n",
    "versions = client.search_model_versions(f\"name='{MODEL_NAME}'\")\n",
    "latest_version = max(int(v.version) for v in versions)\n",
    "print(f\"Latest registered version: v{latest_version}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# @champion → current production\n",
    "client.set_registered_model_alias(name=MODEL_NAME, alias=\"champion\", version=latest_version)\n",
    "print(f\"✅ @champion -> v{latest_version}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# @baseline → permanent v1 anchor (never moves once set)\n",
    "# If v1 was created previously and we're now on v2+, @baseline should already be on v1.\n",
    "# Setting it explicitly is idempotent.\n",
    "client.set_registered_model_alias(name=MODEL_NAME, alias=\"baseline\", version=1)\n",
    "print(f\"✅ @baseline -> v1 (permanent reference)\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Model-level description (renders as Markdown at the top of the registry page)\n",
    "MODEL_DESCRIPTION = \"\"\"\\\n",
    "# DME Fraud Detection — LightGBM\n",
    "\n",
    "**Purpose.** Score Durable Medical Equipment insurance claims with a fraud\n",
    "probability in [0, 1]. Higher = more likely fraudulent.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Training data.** `your-gcp-project.ML_DATASETS.fraud_dme_training_dataset`\n",
    "(2021-01-01 .. 2025-12-31). The `fraud_flag` label is pre-computed upstream\n",
    "from an NPI-level fraud list.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Split.** Time-based 70/15/15 quantile on `clm_thru_dt`. Test set is fully\n",
    "out-of-time.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Inputs.** Pandas DataFrame with claim features. The pyfunc wrapper:\n",
    "- fills `bene_days_last_claim` NaN with 999\n",
    "- replaces inf/-inf/NaN with 0 on numeric columns\n",
    "- selects only trained features by name (extras silently dropped, missing → 0)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Output.** 1D numpy array of P(fraud=1), one per input row.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Load.** `mlflow.pyfunc.load_model(\"models:/your-gcp-project.dme_fraud.dme_lgbm@champion\")`\n",
    "\n",
    "**Aliases.**\n",
    "- `@champion` — current production version\n",
    "- `@baseline` — v1, frozen anchor for regression testing\n",
    "\n",
    "**Owner.** your-email@your-org.com\n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "client.update_registered_model(name=MODEL_NAME, description=MODEL_DESCRIPTION)\n",
    "print(\"✅ Model description updated\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Per-version description\n",
    "client.update_model_version(\n",
    "    name=MODEL_NAME,\n",
    "    version=str(latest_version),\n",
    "    description=(\n",
    "        f\"Trained {datetime.now(timezone.utc).strftime('%Y-%m-%d')} from BQ table {BQ_TABLE}. \"\n",
    "        f\"Run: {run_id}. \"\n",
    "        f\"Validation PR-AUC: {pr_auc:.4f}. \"\n",
    "        f\"Test PR-AUC: {test_pr_auc:.4f}. \"\n",
    "        f\"Test top-3% recall: {metrics['test_top03_recall']:.4f}.\"\n",
    "    ),\n",
    ")\n",
